Question: Is the man skiing or snowboarding?

Reference Answer: skiing

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/248353.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='man')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='skiing')
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='snowboarding')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=COUNT(box=BOX2)
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'skiing' if {ANSWER0} > {ANSWER1} else'snowboarding'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
